--- title: "Cotação do ouro - Parte 4 " subtitle: "Modelos Prophet" author: "Pedro Lima" date: "2023-08-05" categories: [Modelos Estatísticos, Série-Temporal,R] toc: true toc-depth: 3 draft: true --- ::: {.cell} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_a76af237a2ee277a9fa1f2bb8a0cf36e'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-3_da42cf6586779db4fc129bf9135930a1'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-4_f9fad3151b2cd81cbee3812016d570a7'} ```{.r .cell-code} splits <- gold_mean %>% time_series_split( assess = "1 year", cumulative = TRUE ) cv <- gold_mean %>% time_series_cv( assess = 12 * 0.5, initial = 12 * 4, skip = 12 * 1, slice_limit = 6, culmulatime = FALSE ) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-5_4cdeb89aaa059f3e18180c67f3e11235'} ```{.r .cell-code} splits %>% tk_time_series_cv_plan() %>% plot_time_series_cv_plan(mes,media, .facet_ncol = 1, .interactive = FALSE) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-6_f350fa8c0345e5ac75da9bb3e6384729'} ```{.r .cell-code} cv %>% tk_time_series_cv_plan() %>% plot_time_series_cv_plan(mes,media, .facet_ncol = 2, .interactive = FALSE) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ## Modelos ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-7_a903e411b6ed653f0c60ea1e84d9fdee'} ```{.r .cell-code} prothet_mod <- prophet_reg( prior_scale_seasonality = 10 ) %>% set_engine("prophet") %>% fit(media ~ mes, training(splits)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-8_3adb49a37fcfbdacfb461cff7dcdae2a'} ```{.r .cell-code} prothet_boost <- prophet_boost() %>% set_engine("prophet_xgboost") %>% fit(media ~ mes + as.numeric(mes) + factor(month(mes, label = TRUE), ordered = F), data = training(splits)) ``` ::: ## Comparando os modelos ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-9_119cb76a030d30178d3079f52b45f6c9'} ```{.r .cell-code} model_table <- modeltime_table( prothet_mod, prothet_boost ) ``` ::: ## Calibrando ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-10_e4466a2b9d88a5b3378ad0514a842e60'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table <- model_table %>% modeltime_calibrate(testing(splits)) ``` ::: ## Residual ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-11_d6cd239def334f9154e0e2a8fbd32ef6'} ```{.r .cell-code} # calib_table %>% # modeltime_residuals() %>% # plot_modeltime_residuals( # .type = "seasonality", # .interactive = FALSE # ) ``` ::: ## Accuracy ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-12_0fe6610341d8a405b483d45653c37475'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table %>% modeltime_accuracy() ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # A tibble: 2 × 9 .model_id .model_desc .type mae mape mase smape rmse rsq 1 1 PROPHET Test 13.0 7.64 2.82 7.28 14.4 0.635 2 2 PROPHET W/ XGBOOST ERRORS Test 9.38 5.28 2.03 5.43 10.4 0.635 ``` ::: ::: ## Test set visualization ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-13_887be7760d5b76560367e867666eb59e'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table %>% modeltime_forecast( new_data = testing(splits), actual_data = gold_mean ) %>% plot_modeltime_forecast() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ## Validação Cruzada ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-14_f7b3ea477cf1ebd3ca8804de08e6d0f0'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted <- model_table %>% modeltime_fit_resamples( resamples = cv, control = control_resamples(verbose = FALSE) ) resamples_fitted ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # Modeltime Table # A tibble: 2 × 4 .model_id .model .model_desc .resample_results 1 1 PROPHET 2 2 PROPHET W/ XGBOOST ERRORS ``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-15_133004ff7d7ee9911f5d74dc8819fba8'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted %>% plot_modeltime_resamples( .point_size = 3, .point_alpha = 0.8, .interactive = FALSE ) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-15-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-16_eddbe8a9e29c8c983270d76cfe11162d'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted %>% modeltime_resample_accuracy(summary_fns = mean) %>% table_modeltime_accuracy(.interactive = FALSE) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}

``` ::: ::: ## Forecast future ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-17_97ce0f5f9007e0a070aca6a238d6962c'} ```{.r .cell-code} future_forecast_tbl <- calib_table %>% modeltime_refit(gold_mean) %>% modeltime_forecast( h = "1 year", actual_data = gold_mean ) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-18_0478fd0f8e88022fdedd8cc57cb4f9d0'} ```{.r .cell-code} future_forecast_tbl %>% plot_modeltime_forecast() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
